displayName: Golden City Dromos, Prince Faction Headquarters B1F

parameters:
Mansion Guard: As you can see, this is the underground
dungeon. It's hardly used nowadays though.
Prince Rex: You don't have the face of a prisoner.

Imperial Secret Agent Luid: Because I'm thinking of it as a
temporary stay.

Prince Rex: You don't have to worry about torture. You know
that, but at the same time, you know nothing.

Prince Rex: That woman doesn't trust anyone other than
herself, not even my father.
Priestess Sophia: Thank you for your generous treatment.

Priestess Sophia: However, Prince Rex, there may be someone
who acts on their own like the nobleman earlier--

Prince Rex: Are you saying that I cannot control my
subjects?
Priestess Sophia: N-No, it's not like that... I apologize!

Prince Rex: I may have become a bit too harsh, shall we go
back?

Priestess Sophia (The same eyes that stared at me when I was
in trouble, the same eyes that glared at Pido to help me at
that time...)
Priestess Sophia (I am no longer... to you...)
Imperial Secret Agent Luid: ...Amina, can you hear me?
Imperial Secret Agent Luid: Amina, can you hear me?

Luid, the debauched nobleman: Hahaha, you've become quite
good at ignoring your master, haven't you!
Debauched nobleman Luid: Hahaha... Amina, can you hear me?

Young Luid: I am a sentimental person. I still believe that
my mother will return to her appearance from that day.

Young Luid: Are you amazed? This is my genuine emotion,
without any lies or deceit...
Maid Amina: Luid still hasn't apologized.

Young Luid: Amina, I'm sorry! I'm sorry for involving you,
for putting you in danger!
Maid Amina: That's not it, don't you understand?

Luid, my little brother: ...I'm sorry for trying to die,
Amina big sister.

Luid, my little brother: I'm sorry, I'm really sorry, big
sister.

Amina, the older sister: Since you apologized sincerely,
I'll forgive you as a special privilege of being your older
sister.

Amina, the older sister: Promise me that you won't do
anything that would make you die, okay? It's a promise
between you and your big sister Amina.

Amina, the older sister: It's okay to cry, so from now on,
big sister Amina will be by your side.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
実績 お姉ちゃん特権

Imperial Secret Agent Luid: I'm grateful to all of you, but
only as a personal sentiment... Humans are complex beings,
you know.

Maid Amina: Thank you very much. I will now show you how I
can change the mood.

Prince Rex: They are saying that they want to go to the
royal palace together.

Prince Rex: As a premise, there has been absolutely no
approach from Caron's side towards them until today.

Prince Rex: After confirming their true intentions, I want
Sophia to come up to the second floor with me.

Prince Rex: Move them both to the same cell so that they can
have an easier conversation with anyone.

Former Imperial Dark Operative Luid: I didn't properly thank
you for helping me! I might get scolded for saying this, but
thank you, Amina.

Former Imperial Dark Operative Luid: Just as I said! Haha,
I'm truly grateful to be able to have such a foolish
conversation like this.

Former Imperial Dark Operative Luid: It's a shameless
request, but I really want to go to the royal palace on the
day of the decisive battle.
Clea: May I ask for the reason?

Former Imperial Dark Operative Luid: You might find it
laughable, but... for me, Queen Caron... no, my mother is an
important person.

Former Imperial Dark Operative Luid: I think I won't be able
to accept it unless I hear you say, 'You are unnecessary' in
the end...

Mage Relm: Um... it's difficult to say, but... I heard that
there hasn't been any negotiation like a prisoner exchange.

Maid Amina: Luid also understands in his head how Caron
feels about him.

Thief Nora: If that's the case, it'll be harder to
confirm...!

Maid Amina: I believe that everyone here has been fighting
for reasons they want to [accept].

Maid Amina: Even if there is pain and suffering ahead, it
means wanting to have conviction in order to move forward.

Maid Amina: Luid is the same. He also wants to understand
and take a step forward.
Prince Rex: Have you been able to assess the situation?

Clea: I believe I should be taken on the day of the decisive
battle.

Clea: If Luid's strong attachment to Caron disappears, if we
can defeat Caron before that attachment fades...

Clea: Luid-san will aim for Prince Rex's life for the rest
of his life.
Clea: ...Just like I used to be.

Clea: Luid-san's goal has already changed from wanting to be
useful to Caron to wanting to satisfy himself.

Prince Rex: If your thoughts are correct, then I believe we
should execute him instead of taking him to the royal
palace.

Clea: Amina-san is the one who requested the Guild to betray
the Imperial Dark Division and break Luid-san's curse.

Clea: She is not blindly on Luid-san's side. While
considering Luid-san's goals, she will definitely be on the
prince's side.

Clea: They are very reliable escorts. We can assert that
without a doubt, as we fought alongside them.

Prince Rex: They will not aim for my life, on the contrary,
they will become excellent escorts. Is this acceptable?

Prince Rex: If they were to betray me... if such a situation
were to occur, how would you take responsibility?

Clea: I will immediately cut him down and take
responsibility for it with my own life.

Prince Rex: Understood. If you meet certain conditions, I
will forgive you. As a minimum requirement, you must fully
obey our instructions.

Prince Rex: Luid, after accepting your request, I want to
confirm the members of the Imperial Dark Division and
Caron's combat capabilities again.

Former Imperial Dark Division member Luid: Understood, I
will follow your orders.
Prince Rex: Next is you, Clea.

Prince Rex: I heard that you have a close relationship with
the noble Casaro. Make sure to extract something that will
give us an advantage in battle from him.

Prince Rex: That is the condition that will take the two of
you to the royal palace.
Clea: Understood, leave it to me.

Prince Rex: This is not a continuation of our previous
conversation, but...

Prince Rex: I envy Sophia because she has made the decision
to become a good friend to the king.
Priestess Sophia: They are friends who are too good for me.
Priestess Sophia: Hehe, then I shall be on my way.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
